verbose_text: Through biliary ductal cell isolation, it is possible to generate cholangiocyte like organoids (Chol-Org), which differ greatly from Hep-Org, as shown through RNA analysis, and through lineage tracing, loosely indicates a similarity between primary hepatocytes and Hep-Org, however, Hep-Orgs have shown decreased HNF4a and albumin expression, 2- and 4-fold decrease, respectively, whilst Chol-Orgs demonstrated> 1000-fold decrease [XREF_BIBR].
